                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5799" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0288</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7765 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">崔班长的创新初体验：S邮区中心局一线员工创新管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The first experience of innovation of monitor Cui: Innovative management of front-line employees of the Central Bureau of S Postal District</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵会娟，施毅，李佳荣，李怡宁，南玉婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国邮政集团有限公司陕西省西安邮区中心局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">基层部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工创新行为；创新过程；员工创新管理；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">employee innovation behavior，innovation process，employee innovation management </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了S邮区中心局一线维修技术员崔班长，发现上线不久的新型小件分拣系统频繁出现卡件问题，造成生产线运行中断，维修压力大，生产运行效率下降。为了改善这个局面，满足业务旺季生产运行质量要求，在求助同行和供应商无果的情况下，崔班长只好尝试自己想办法解决，从此开启了他的创新体验之旅。崔班长首先认真分析卡件的原因，主动学习相关技术知识、寻求同事和其他技术人员帮助，有了解决卡片问题的初步构想，然后在技术人员帮助和自己的努力下完成了设计草图，接着在郑局赞赏和鼎力帮助之下，一步步完成了项目立项，在项目实施过程中遇到组建团队难题，新方案技术不稳定等问题，最终在自已的努力与团队的支持下，克服种种困难完成了工艺改造项目，并获得省邮政公司科技成果奖。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case tells about the front-line maintenance technician Cui of the S postal district central office. He found that the new small parts sorting system that was recently launched frequently had card problems, which caused the production line to be interrupted, the maintenance pressure was high, and the production and operation efficiency was reduced. In order to improve this situation and meet the production and operation quality requirements of the business peak season, in the case of seeking help from peers and suppliers to no avail, monitor Cui had to try to find a solution by himself, thus starting his journey of innovative experience. Class leader Cui firstly analyzed the causes of the stuck pieces, took the initiative to learn relevant technical knowledge, sought help from colleagues and other technicians, and had a preliminary idea to solve the card problem, and then completed the design sketch with the help of technicians and his own efforts. Under Zheng Ju’s appreciation and full help, the project was established step by step. During the implementation of the project, it encountered difficulties in team formation and technical instability of the new solution. Finally, with its own efforts and the support of the team, it overcame various difficulties and completed it. Completed the technological transformation project, and won the Provincial Post Company Science and Technology Achievement Award. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《技术创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">个体心理与行为、员工创新行为、创新管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
